Requirements for Elevator system 

1  multiple elevator cars and floors in the building.

2  can have a maximum of 15 floors and three elevators.

3  can move up or down or be in an idle state.

4 door can only be opened when it is in an idle state.

5  passes through each floor.

6  have buttons to call an elevator car and to specify whether the passenger wants to go up or down.

7  should have buttons to go to every floor. There should be buttons to open or close the lift doors.

8 elevator display screen is there outside 

9 elvator display screen inside for capacity 

10 panels and buttons are there on each floor.

11 passengers can go to differennt or same floors 

12 can control elevator and door movements 

13 send suitable car to passenger 

14 can carry max of 8 perrsons 

Components of an elevator system
Button
Elevator panel and hall panel
Display
Door
Elevator car
Floor
Building
Elevator system
Enumerations






